title: Stepping Into Your Divine Destiny | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Stepping Into Your Divine Destiny | Joel Osteen
description:
Deep down you have potential that has not yet been released. God didn’t create anyone as ordinary. You are fearfully and wonderfully made, fully loaded and totally equipped, with all you need to fulfill your purpose.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
